  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Supercross Freestyle is a dirt bike racing game. The game features three game modes: Freestyle, Supercross and Arcade. Freestyle is all about making impressive jumps and tricks with your bike. Supercross and Arcade are racing modes, where Arcade has different courses and power-ups that can change the odds. The game features 24 different tracks and 16 different tricks.",
